commit.message:
correct input-mmap-port so that works correctly with Java resources

Also added a few simple recette tests and updated
input_port.rgc_enlarge_buffer_size so that it matched the behavior of
seen in the c-backend's crgc buffer handling

Add support for input-mmap-port to jvm backend

Also fixed the c-backend's implementation of bgl_input_mmap_seek and
enabled the reopening of input-mmap-ports
